{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<address>","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O <strong>elemento HTML&nbsp;<code>&lt;address&gt;</code></strong>&nbsp;fornece&nbsp;informações de contato para seu ancestral <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> mais próximo; no segundo caso, ele se aplica ao documento inteiro.</p>\n\n<p>A informação de contato fornecida por um conteúdo do elemento&nbsp;<code>&lt;address&gt;</code>&nbsp;pode tomar qualquer forma que é apropriada para o contexto, e pode incluir qualquer tipo de informação de contato necessária, como endereço físico, URL, email, telefone, mídia social, coordenadas geográficas, por aí vai. Deve incluir o nome da pessoa, grupo, ou organização para qual as informações de contato se referem.</p>\n\n<p><code>&lt;address&gt;</code>&nbsp;pode ser usado em uma variedade de contextos, como fornecer informação de contato de uma empresa no header da página, ou indicar o autor de um artigo incluindo um elemento&nbsp;<code>&lt;address&gt;</code>&nbsp;dentro do <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Categoria de conteúdo</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>, conteúdo palpável.</li>\n <li><dfn>Conteúdo permitido</dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>, mas sem nenhum elemento <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&lt;address&gt;</span> aninhado, e sem conteúdo de cabeçalho (<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>), e nem conteúdo de seção como (<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>), e sem<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> ou o elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Omissão de tag</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn>Elementos-pai permitidos</dfn> Qualquer elemento que aceite <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\">conteúdo de fluxo</a>, exceto os elementos&nbsp;&lt;address&gt; (de acordo com o princípio lógico da simetria, se a tag &lt;address&gt;, como pai, não pode ter elemento &lt;address&gt; como filho, então o mesmo conteúdo &lt;address&gt; não pode ter&nbsp;tag &lt;address&gt; como pai).</li>\n <li>&nbsp;</li>\n <li><dfn>Regras ARIA permitidas</dfn> Nenhuma</li>\n <li><dfn>Interface DOM</dfn> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>. Antes do Gecko 2.0 (Firefox 4), Gecko implementava este elemento usando a interface <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Este elemento inclui somente os </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">atributos globais</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_de_uso","title":"Notas de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Para representar um endereço arbitrário, um que não é relacionado à informação para contato, use um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a> ao invés do elemento &lt;address&gt;.</li>\n <li>Este elemento não deve conter mais informação além da informação de contato, como uma data de publicação (a qual pertence ao elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>).</li>\n <li>Tipicamente um elemento &lt;address&gt; pode ser posicionado dentro do elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a> da seção atual, se houver um.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code>  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>address</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Voce pode contatar o autor em <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.somedomain.com/contact<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>www.somedomain.com<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Se encontrar qualquer bug, por favor <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>mailto:webmaster@somedomain.com<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>contate o administrador do site<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Você tambem pode querer nos visitar:<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Mozilla Foundation<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    1981 Landings Drive<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Building K<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    Mountain View, CA 94043-0801<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    USA\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>address</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resultado","title":"Resultado","isH3":true,"content":"<address>Voce pode contatar o autor em <a href=\"http://www.somedomain.com/contact\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">www.somedomain.com</a>.<br>\nSe encontrar qualquer bug, por favor <a href=\"mailto:webmaster@somedomain.com\">contate o administrador do site</a>.<br>\nVocê tambem pode querer nos visitar:<br>\nMozilla Foundation<br>\n1981 Landings Drive<br>\nBuilding K<br>\nMountain View, CA 94043-0801<br>\nUSA</address>\n\n<address>&nbsp;</address>\n\n<p>Embora o elemento <code>address</code> exiba o texto com o mesmo estilo padrão que os elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, ele é mais apropriado de ser usado quando se lida com informação de contato, já que ele fornece informação semântica adicional.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/sections.html#the-address-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;address&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/sections.html#the-address-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;address&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/global.html#h-7.5.6\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of '&lt;address&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Funcionalidade</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7 or earlier)</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>5.12</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Funcionalidade</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mini</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>1.0 (1.7)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_também","title":"Ver também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Outros elementos relacionados à seção: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>;</li>\n <li class=\"last\"><a class=\"deki-ns current page-not-created\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Seções e delineamento de um documento HTML5</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Notas de uso","id":"notas_de_uso"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Ver também","id":"ver_também"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <address> fornece informações de contato para seu ancestral <article> ou <body> mais próximo; no segundo caso, ele se aplica ao documento inteiro.","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<address>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<address>: The Contact Address element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<address>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<address> : l'élément d'adresse de contact","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<address>: 連絡先要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<address>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<address>: Element Adresu Kontaktowego","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<address>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<address>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/address","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/address/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address","title":"<address>"}],"pageTitle":"<address> - HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}